package: SnapReview
author: Tony Lyons
version: 1.5
rv: 3.0

modes:
  - file: NotesOverlay
    load: immediate

mu:
  - file: notes_dialog
    load: immediate
  - file: clipboard
    load: immediate

description: |
  SnapReview notes overlay plugin for OpenRV.
  Adds SnapReview menu for adding text annotations and exporting review packages.

  Features:
  - Add Note (Shift+N) - Multi-line text input with copy/paste support
  - White text with black outline for readability on any background
  - Smart text wrapping and vertical stacking
  - Timeline markers on frames with notes
  - Notes persist in RVPaint node properties (survives session save/autosave)
  - Copy Notes (Ctrl+Shift+C) - exports all notes for current source
  - Save Review (Ctrl+Shift+S) - exports session, notes file, and annotated frames
